OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781240641
OL,3,CFly tipper prosecuted for illegally
OL,4,Cdumping construction waste
OL,6,FA fly tipper has been prosecuted by
OL,7,FWiltshire Council for illegally
OL,8,Fdumping construction waste.
OL,10,FAshleigh Witts, from Swindon, pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty to fly tipping and failing to
OL,12,Fproduce waste transfer documentation.
OL,14,FHe was given a Community Order, told
OL,15,Fto complete 210 hours of unpaid work,
OL,16,Fand pay #1,114 in fines, costs and
OL,17,Fvictim surcharges.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
