PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781240641
OL,3,CFly tipper prosecuted for illegally
OL,4,Cdumping construction waste
OL,6,FThe prosecution followed an
OL,7,Finvestigation after a large fly tip
OL,8,Fwas reported on land off the A419 at
OL,9,FLatton, near Cricklade, on March 23,
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FOfficers found the site filled with
OL,13,Fconstruction waste, including felt,
OL,14,Fchipboard and tiles, which Witts had
OL,15,Ftravelled through the county to dump.
OL,17,FThe waste was linked to a roofing
OL,18,Fbusiness in Swindon, called ARW
OL,19,FProperty Services.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781240641
OL,3,CFly tipper prosecuted for illegally
OL,4,Cdumping construction waste
OL,6,FThe company helped officers to trace
OL,7,FWitts, and in light of this
OL,8,Fcooperation, no further action was
OL,9,Ftaken against it.
OL,11,FDespite multiple requests, Witts did
OL,12,Fnot attend an interview until several
OL,13,Fmonths later, where he gave no comment
OL,14,Fresponses.
OL,16,FHe also failed to provide legally
OL,17,Frequired waste transfer notes and did
OL,18,Fnot pay two fixed penalty notices.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
