OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781240641
OL,3,CFly tipper prosecuted for illegally
OL,4,Cdumping construction waste
OL,6,FWiltshire Councillor Martin Smith,
OL,7,FCabinet Member for Highways,
OL,8,FStreetscene and Flooding said the
OL,9,Fsentence "sends a very clear message".
OL,11,FHe said: "We will take action against
OL,12,Fanyone committing environmental crime
OL,13,Fwithin our county.
OL,15,F"Mr Witts was trusted to dispose of
OL,16,Fwaste responsibly, but instead chose
OL,17,Fto dump it illegally, harming our
OL,18,Fenvironment and local communities.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
