OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781240641
OL,3,CFly tipper prosecuted for illegally
OL,4,Cdumping construction waste
OL,6,F"On top of that, he failed to operate
OL,7,Flegally as a waste carrier and ignored
OL,8,Fmultiple opportunities to cooperate
OL,9,Fwith our investigation."
